elements.name: Patient can enroll for monthly membership while registration

steps.name: Patient should be navigated to invite code page and able to see "see our memberships scheme" option
Patient click on see our membership scheme button
Patient should be navigated to membership page with "Memberships" title
Click on LGP membership scheme button
Patient should be able to view monthly membership scheme
Patient select monthly scheme and click on Apply for Membership button
Patient should be navigated to disclaimer page with "Disclaimer" and "Fees"
Patient accept conditions and click on Apply for Membership
Patient should be navigated to register page with title "Register"
User should be in Confirm details page
